(fifthQuint)Evaluation of Spa Medicine on the Example of Comprehensive Therapy in the Spa Resort Przerzeczyn Zdroj.

 The observation was conducted during 21 days of medicinal stays in the health resort of Przerzeczyn Zdroj.

 The treatment included a comprehensive therapy: redon-sulfide baths, partial mud baths, kinesitherapy, terrain therapy, dry massage, laser therapy, low-frequency magnetic field, ultrasonotherapy, cryotherapy, electrotherapy, light therapy.

 The study group consisted of patients with joint or back pain due to osteoarthritis or degenerative disc disease.

